    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8046-b4db-c75d2700c6da",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Pixel Watch 3 was Google's third-generation wearable. With growing competition in the health and fitness space, we needed to ",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "transition from a data tracking and dashboard product",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " to a ",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "coaching product",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " in order to differentiate through intelligence and guidance.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8097-9a6c-fc3c54f8fb8b",
      "type": "quote",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How might we redefine the fitness product from a data analyzer to a proactive, personalized, and motivating coaching experience?",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-80a7-975f-dc1c49cca58e",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Defined product strategy: ",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8083-973c-deecf8fad962",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Start with one segment and expand later",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-80f8-9fa4-c86ccf1091e1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "I worked with PM partners to define a strategy for Pixel Watch 3: build a world-class wearable for fitness enthusiasts first, starting with cardio experiences powered by heart-rate advantages. I led an end-to-end vision across watch and mobile with a one-year outlook to align teams and execution.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8027-8d88-cb48a487beff",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "I co-created the product and design strategy for the fitness area on watch.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-80c1-a7a4-eb50e4f41287",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Introduced structured workout tracking",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-80eb-8b8a-fa85fc6af226",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "From field research, we learned runners use different training methods. I proposed a structured workout model that enables segments and customization. It required a major shift in infrastructure and mental model, and created a foundation for long-term personalization across workout types.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8036-960a-f0eb65c6b047",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Standard workout ",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The entire workout is one session.",
